snippet: Louis Oosthuizen birdied four of the last five holes for a six-under-par 64 and a share of the third-round lead with Brendon Todd at the Byron Nelson Championship in Irving, Tex.
abstract: Louis Oosthuizen shares third-round lead with Brendon Todd at the Byron Nelson Championship in Irving, Tex; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Louis Oosthuizen birdied four of the last five holes for a six-under-par 64 and a share of the third-round lead with Brendon Todd at the Byron Nelson Championship in Irving, Tex.

headline.main: Tie for Lead at Byron Nelson Championship
